Description:
    Copy the views from importable so you can override them

    Include NAME to create the templates in a subdirectory. These will apply only to the mapper with a corresponding name.

Example:
    rails generate importable:views

    This will create:
        app/views/importable
        app/views/importable/_errors.html.erb
        app/views/importable/_extras.html.erb
        app/views/importable/spreadsheets
        app/views/importable/spreadsheets/_actions.html.erb
        app/views/importable/spreadsheets/_choose_worksheet_step.html.erb
        app/views/importable/spreadsheets/_upload_file_step.html.erb
        app/views/importable/spreadsheets/new.html.erb
        app/views/importable/spreadsheets/show.html.erb
        app/views/importable/resources
        app/views/importable/resources/_actions.html.erb
        app/views/importable/resources/new.html.erb
        app/views/importable/resources/show.html.erb

    rails generate importable:views foos

    This will create:
        app/views/foos/importable
        app/views/foos/importable/_errors.html.erb
        app/views/foos/importable/_extras.html.erb
        app/views/foos/importable/spreadsheets
        app/views/foos/importable/spreadsheets/_actions.html.erb
        app/views/foos/importable/spreadsheets/_choose_worksheet_step.html.erb
        app/views/foos/importable/spreadsheets/_upload_file_step.html.erb
        app/views/foos/importable/spreadsheets/new.html.erb
        app/views/foos/importable/spreadsheets/show.html.erb
        app/views/foos/importable/resources
        app/views/foos/importable/resources/_actions.html.erb
        app/views/foos/importable/resources/new.html.erb
        app/views/foos/importable/resources/show.html.erb
